---
title: Saucy Bacon Cheeseburgers and Fried Onions with Sweet Potato Wedges and BBQ Fry Sauce
description: These burgers pack a flavourful punch thanks to cheddar cheese, savoury fried onions and a DIY BBQ fry sauce. Don't worry, there's enough sauce to dip the roasted sweet potatoes in too!
